description: This file is the entry point for a React web application, responsible for rendering the root component <App /> into the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports core React libraries, styling, and the main App component.

methods.name: createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root to enable rendering of React components into the DOM.

methods.name: render
methods.description: Renders the React component <App /> wrapped in <React.StrictMode> into the DOM.
